brief summary of my life

i was born in trois-rivi&egrave;res, a town of about 50000, roughly halfway
between montr&eacute;al et qu&eacute;bec city, where i lived until july 1984.
since then, i have been living in ch&acirc;teauguay, in the south-west of
montr&eacute;al, a town of about 40000.

i went to these schools (i welcome e-mail from old school pals).


ecole primaire cardinal-roy, trois-rivi&egrave;res, 1976-1982;
s&eacute;minaire st-joseph, trois-rivi&egrave;res, 1982-1984;
polyvalente (now ecole secondaire) louis-philippe par&eacute,
	ch&acirc;teauguay, 1984-1987;
cegep maisonneuve, montr&eacute;al, 1987-1990
	(dec in pure and applied science);
mcgill university, montr&eacute;al, 1990-1993 (b.sc. in computer science);
ditto, 1994-, (m.sc. in computer science).


 
